value.0: This armor is created from scales discarded by Galdor the Gold. It is imbued with a portion of the creature's mystical might.

The dream of every paladin is to claim his own Holy Avenger. These blessed weapons are found only amongst the most elite paladins, whose lives have been fully dedicated to the pursuits of their gods. One famous paladin described his weapon as his best and last friend in every situation. When peace fails, the Holy Avenger becomes the embodiment of the law.

This specific weapon was created by Galdor the gold for those of his League of the Golden Scale. It is given to only the most worthy defenders of the realm.
This helmet was created by Galdor the Gold, and creates a link between him and teh wearer. Wearing this helm enables the wearer to share some of Galdor's qualities.

This is the key to the Guild Hall for the League of the Golden Scale. A benevolent guild formed to protect the realm of Nordock from encroaching evil. Guild members swear fealty to Galdor the Gold, sworn protector of Benzor.
